<body>
  <%- include("partials/header") %>
  <main>
    <h2>Site Agreement</h2>
    <p>This website provides a place for people to share reviews, experiences, and questions about hairstyling services and products. By submitting content or using the site, you agree to follow these guidelines and use the platform respectfully.</p>
    <h3>Reviews and Questions</h3>
    <p>Visitors may submit reviews or questions about services or products. Reviews should reflect honest, real experiences and questions should be respectful and relevant. Spam, harassment, hate speech, and false information is not allowed. Any review that goes against these guidelines will be deleted.</p>
    <h3>Price Estimates</h3>
    <p>Any price estimates shown on the website are general estimates only. They will be based on typical service ranges and should not be considered guaranteed quotes. Actual prices may vary depending on the service, hair type, time required, and other factors.</p>
    <h3>Privacy</h3>
    <p>While this website does not have a login, any information you submit when posting a review or a question will be stored and be publicly visible on the website to all users.</p>
    <p>By submitting a review, question, photo, or other content, you confirm that you have the right to share it and grant permission for it to be displayed and used as part of the platform.</p>
    <h3>Use of the Website</h3>
    <p>The information on this website, including reviews, responses, and price estimates, is provided for general informational purposes only. While we aim to maintain a helpful and respectful community, we cannot guarantee the accuracy or completeness of user-submitted information.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="/agree" class="form-box">
      <button>I Agree</button>
    </form>
  </main>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>